      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Chop your<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
