          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your<strong> chicken thighs</strong> dry with kitchen paper then add, skin side up, to the baking tray[s], nestled amongst the vegetables</p><p>Top the chicken with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 30-35 min or until the veg is roasted and tender and the chicken is cooked through and golden (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spring roast chicken tray bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1712846982056-x200.jpg",
