            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the tray bake is almost ready, boil half a kettle</p><p>Combine your<strong> gravy base </strong>with the<strong> remaining dried thyme </strong>and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, whisk thoroughly</p><p>Put it in the<strong> microwave </strong>and cook for 30-40 secs or until thickened and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> thyme gravy</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
